<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="TVM1.5.7">
<l>aṭiyēṉ ciṟiya ñāṉatta ṉaṟita lārkku mariyāṉaik</l>
<l>kaṭicēr taṇṇan tuḻāykkaṇṇi puṉaintāṉ ṟaṉṉaik kaṇṇaṉaic</l>
<l>ceṭiyā rākkai yaṭiyāraic cērta ṟīrkkun tirumālai</l>
<l>yaṭiyēṉ kāṇpā ṉalaṟṟuva ṉitaṉiṉ mikkō rayarvuṇṭē</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>I [his] servant am of little knowledge. The one who is difficult to know for anybody,</l>
<l>the one who is decorated with a fragrant cool Tulsi chaplet, Kaṇṇaṉ,</l>
<l>Tirumāl who end [his] servants’ joining the bodies of sinful/troubled people,</l>
<l>in order to see him I [his] servant keep talking. Is there any oblivion greater than this?</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
</text>
